Opening another wireshark in macOS:
open -n /Applications/Wireshark.app

Filter that works for string and Hexadecimal:
frame contains "candy"
or 00:01 format for Hex.

FTP
To convert a FTP stream to a file:
1. Filter by ftp-data, notice the file size
2. follow stream
3. Note the file type and convert to Raw on the popup
4. Save the file, ensuring to correctly set the filetype.
